            <p class="lead">The ALX mentors evaluation system is a comprehensive and structured approach designed to assess the performance and effectiveness of mentors within the ALX platform. ALX is a digital learning platform that provides professional development and mentorship opportunities to individuals seeking to enhance their skills and advance their careers.</p>
