                <h2 id="librariesTitle">Design Goal of the AMPES</h2>
                <p>
                   The ALX mentors evaluation system is designed to be ongoing and iterative, allowing for continuous improvement and learning. It provides mentors with valuable insights into their strengths and areas for development, helping them refine their mentoring techniques and strategies. The evaluation system also offers a feedback loop that promotes accountability, transparency, and quality assurance within the mentorship program.
                        <p>
