                <p>
                    By implementing the mentors evaluation system, ALX aims to ensure that mentees receive exceptional guidance from mentors who are well-equipped to support their learning journey. The system facilitates a culture of continuous improvement and excellence among mentors, ultimately enhancing the overall effectiveness of the mentorship program within the ALX platform.
